---
title: Red Pesto & Chorizo Fettuccine with Lemon Pangrattato & Rocket Salad
description: Sometimes the simplest things in life provide the greatest joy… like a big satisfying bowl of pesto pasta. We've added irresistible chunks of chorizo, crunchy lemon pangrattato and a side of rocket, because we just can’t help taking things up a notch!
